                    <td class="details_table"><b><span style="font-family:'gotham_bookregular', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:16px;"> General</span></b><br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">1. What is AEO Rewards?</span><br /><br />
                                AEO Rewards is a loyalty program whereby members in select markets earn points on purchases (after Discounts and before Taxes and Fees) made at American Eagle Outfitters and Aerie. For every 1,000 points earned a $5 Reward is issued, good for use at American Eagle Outfitters and Aerie stores. Additional benefits include buy 5 bras, get 1 free, buy 5 pairs of jeans, get 1 free, an exclusive birthday offer and members-only sales and events. At this time, the program is limited to select markets, but stay tuned for changes and more opportunities to participate.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">2. How can I join the program?</span><br /><br />
                                There is no fee to join AEO Rewards and you qualify for this program if you are in a participating market and a US resident 13 years of age and older. Ask your store associate to enroll you or call 1-800-340-0532 to find out if you are eligible to participate. You'll need to provide and validate an email address to use so that we can send you your rewards. You can also provide a mobile number if you'd like us to text your rewards to you. Standard text messaging rates apply.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">3. I'm currently a member of AERewards. Do I have to do anything different to participate in the new enhanced AEO Rewards?</span><br /><br />
                               If you are a member of our program or have an AEO credit card account or Aerie credit card account, and you reside in a participating market, you are already enrolled and all you need to do is provide and validate an email address so that we can send you your rewards. Just provide your email address to a store associate or call Customer Service at 1-800-340-0532.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">4. Why is my email address required in order to participate in AEO Rewards?</span><br /><br />
                            In order to send you your rewards, your email address is required. We do not mail rewards as our program is paperless, and want to make sure that your earned rewards get to the right place.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">5. Why do I have to validate my email address?</span><br /><br />Validating your email address ensures that we have the correct information on file for your account, so that rewards are sent to the right place.<br /><br />
                           
                            <span class="bold">7. How do I update my account profile or check my balance?</span><br /><br />Your account information can be accessed at <a href="http://www.aeorewards.com" target="_self" class="link_body">www.aeorewards.com</a> or call 1-800-340-0532. If you were an AERewards member previously, your login remains the same. If you need to create an account, use the email you used to signed up for AEO Rewards and create a password to login to your account.<br /><br />
