                            <span class="bold">8. What's a qualifying purchase?</span><br /><br />
                            When purchasing in-store or online, the qualifying amount for earning points is the transaction total for merchandise, excluding Gift Card purchases or charitable items, after any discounts or Rewards have been applied and before sales or other taxes, state fees, shipping charges (collectively &dagger;úTaxes and Fees&dagger;ù). But don't worry; you'll still earn points if you pay for your merchandise with a gift card.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">9. Do I earn points for my online purchases?</span><br /><br />Yes! You earn the same number of points whether you shop in-store at American Eagle Outfitters or Aerie or online at AE.com or Aerie.com. Just be sure to log in before you complete your purchase.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">10. How do I become a Silver AEO Rewards member?</span><br /><br />If you spend $250 USD or more (excluding gift cards and after Taxes and Fees) at American Eagle Outfitters and/or Aerie in a calendar year, you'll automatically be given Reward Silver status starting with your next purchase. Your status will be good to the end of the year and for the next calendar year as well!<br /><br />
                            
                            Please note that the dollar amount from returned merchandise will decrease the purchases applied towards tier status. If a return decreases the amount of purchases below $250 during the same calendar year you first earn status, your status will be re-evaluated and you may no longer have Reward Silver status.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">11. What do I get for becoming a Silver AEO Rewards member?</span><br /><br />
                            You earn 4 extra points for $1 USD of qualifying purchases at American Eagle Outfitters stores, Aerie stores, AEO Factory stores, online and via direct phone orders. Plus, you will receive special offers throughout the year.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">12. Are there any other benefits of being a member of AEO Rewards?</span><br /><br />
                            Yes! As a member, if you purchase 5 bras (excluding bandeaus, bralettes and sports bras) you will get 1 bra free! You can redeem the free bra reward at Aerie stores and online.<br /><br />
