                            Once you have earned these rewards, they will be sent to you via email or text, depending on your preferences.<br /><br />
                            You will also receive a special birthday offer, which you can use anytime during your birth month. These birthday offers are sent at the beginning of your birthday month, so make sure to watch out for it in your inbox!<br /><br />


