                            <span class="bold">15. What do my points get me?</span><br /><br />
                           For every 1,000 points you earn, you will receive a $5 Reward. Rewards are automatically issued 14-20 days after you reach 1,000 points, or after you have earned a free bra or denim item, Rewards are sent directly to your email address, so make sure your email address on file is up-to-date. Rewards must be used within 45 days of being issued and are non-transferable. Rewards can be used with other offers including other $5 Rewards or your Free Jeans and Free Bras Rewards. A maximum of five $5 Rewards may be used together at one time. You can also provide a mobile number if you want us to text you your Rewards. If you think you should have received a reward, but did not, please contact us at 1-800-340-0532.<br /><br />
                            <span class="bold">16. How do I redeem a Reward?</span><br /><br />
